prompts.frontCover: A whimsical, flat 2D cartoon illustration for a birthday card, rendered in a dreamy fantasy art style. The scene features a magnificent, slightly grumpy cartoon griffin perched majestically atop a giant, beautifully decorated birthday cake. The griffin, with fluffy, ethereal feathers in pastel rainbow hues and shimmering gold highlights, is wearing a tiny, comically askew birthday party hat. It has a humorous, unimpressed expression, looking directly at the viewer as if guarding its sugary throne. The cake is a multi-layered fantasy creation with pastel pink and lavender frosting, cascading edible glitter, and glowing, magical mushrooms sprouting from its sides instead of candles. The entire scene is set against a soft, ethereal background of swirling pearlescent clouds and floating, glowing motes of light. In the center of the image, written in a beautiful, readable, and elegant handwritten cursive script, is the text: "I was told there would be cake." The overall tone is charming, humorous, and magical.
